/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.0 596.0 Tm (- Name it: "This is a cold call - I will be quick and you can hang up any time.") Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 582.0 Tm (- Earn the next ten seconds with one specific, relevant reason.) Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 568.0 Tm (- Ask permission to continue instead of barreling ahead.) Tj
