1 0 0 1 56.0 517.0 Tm (Guarded prospects expect a rehearsed pitch and are ready to decline it. Naming the call) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 503.0 Tm (for what it is breaks that script and treats them like an adult, which often buys a few) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 489.0 Tm (real seconds of attention. The goal is not to trap them into listening - it is to make) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 475.0 Tm (staying an easy, informed choice.) Tj
