1 0 0 1 56.0 451.0 Tm (Worked example) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 56.0 434.0 Tm ("Hi Alex - I will be honest, this is a cold call, so feel free to hang up. I called) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 420.0 Tm (because your job posting mentioned onboarding delays, and that is the exact thing I help) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 406.0 Tm (ops teams shorten. Can I take thirty seconds to explain why I thought of you, and then) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 392.0 Tm (you decide if it is worth continuing?") Tj
